text_block_list.name: Monologue
text_block_list.text:
Summer camp has come once again, but<n>Symboli
Rudolf seems far more relaxed<n>this time around.

text_block_list.name: Monologue
text_block_list.text:
She's perfectly content to watch the<n>curtain rise
on the camp as nothing more<n>than another
student of Tracen<n>Academy.
